Package: cislongitudinal
Title: Access the CIS Longitudinal Dataset
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Hector", "Meleiro", email = "hmeleiros@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-4468-2197"))
Description: Provides tools to download, cache, update, inspect, and query the
    longitudinal Centro de Investigaciones Sociologicas (CIS) dataset published
    by Spain Electoral Project as a Parquet file. Queries use Arrow and dplyr so
    filters and column selection can be pushed down before collecting data into R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/hmeleiro/cislongitudinal,
    https://cislongitudinal.spainelectoralproject.com/
BugReports: https://github.com/hmeleiro/cislongitudinal/issues
